{"tid":727761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大馬傳媒：前首相納吉涉貪被捕","createTime":"2018-07-03T09:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T20:25:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"42036f5c871b2fd99bb38054145f5b0067097e09","tid":727761,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/NA_J2g4c_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FNA_J2g4c_1200x0.png&h=aca8ffe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞前首相納吉下台後，因其涉貪醜聞而遭受調查。據多個媒體報道指，納吉今日在家中遭上門拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n《當今大馬》引述反貪會及警方消息，指納吉是今午在吉隆玻住家被捕，已被帶往反貪會總部。反貪會主席蘇克里暫時拒絕證實納吉被捕的消息，但就透露自己正跟總警長開會，「我們即將出聲明。」<br />\n<br />\n新加坡亞洲新聞台則引述納吉的家庭律師，證實納吉已經被捕，料明日將會被正式起訴。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述三個消息來源指出，納吉在今日在被捕，案件與他任內創立的國家主權財富基金一馬發展公司（1MDB）的資金流失有關。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息兩個接近納吉家庭的消息指，納吉在今日在家中被補，其中一個消息指，納吉明天會現身法庭，被正式檢控。<br />\n<br />\n納吉因私人戶口接獲26億令吉巨額資金（近46億港元），捲入國家投資公司一馬公司案。國際調查顯示，這筆26億令吉資金源自一馬公司，惟納吉宣稱這是沙地王室成員的「捐款」。納吉多次強調清白，而總檢察長阿班迪也指，調查顯示納吉無罪。至上月納吉所領導的國陣在選舉中落敗下台，隨即被禁止離開大馬，其寓所亦被警方徹夜搜查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92-%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E5%89%8D%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E7%B4%8D%E5%90%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%25B4%258D%25E5%2590%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=Hbpg4j%2F5NhQYtgRbQA9tJL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f66c44fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%25B4%258D%25E5%2590%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=e49e4184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92-%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E5%89%8D%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E7%B4%8D%E5%90%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/</a>"},{"pid":"3ba18952c9e07d6f0cb52c7ca8364cd207539f1d","tid":727761,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"清算了....收左支共咁多扺撚死"},{"pid":"503891a318dfdc20986632222ccd1332a10a9c95","tid":727761,"uid":6372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"6a319053ee3d369ee6028d52e03b7f152225a962","tid":727761,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7cc8d443d8126af2a7b41d34817b19e709be07","tid":727761,"uid":16676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"佢都預左<br />\n大選完已經即時想走佬, 比人計算到揾籍口去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ad7b009c9bfe21f46c78dee0e4355650050bfe","tid":727761,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d7cc8d443d8126af2a7b41d34817b19e709be07","tid":727761,"uid":16676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"佢都預左<br />\n大選完已經即時想走佬, 比人計算到揾籍口去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:01:42.000Z","msg":"未宣布賽果之前就要走<br />\n再之後根本無可能走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d693189dec4a0403f68f24ca4fb2d45789aba04","tid":727761,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4455995a8ebb9bed98609592d4285076ff4f9e83","tid":727761,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"（早報訊）馬來西亞首相馬哈迪聲稱，馬國政府即將就一馬公司案和蒙古女郎命案，提控前首相納吉。<br />\n<br />\n當今大馬引述馬新社的報道指出，馬哈迪在印度尼西亞會晤旅居當地的馬國人時表示，政府調查一馬公司案和蒙古女郎命案後，收集到重大證據。<br />\n<br />\n他說：&ldquo;我認為，他（納吉）即將被帶往法庭。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n馬哈迪補充，當局將會重審蒙古女郎案。他指出：&ldquo;（針對一馬公司資金濫用案），有些人說當局沒對付納吉，甚至還以前首相身份禮遇他&hellip;&hellip;若你要將一宗案件帶上法庭，你需要有充足證據，確保不會輸掉官司。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n馬哈迪說，警方搜查三間與納吉相關的柏威年高級公寓所後查獲價值10億令吉（約3億4000萬新元）的珠寶，而這還不包括現款。<br />\n<br />\n早前，馬哈迪透露，檢調單位將研究以挪用政府資金、貪汙和賄賂多項罪名，提控前首相納吉涉及一馬公司舞弊。<br />\n<br />\n至於蒙古女郎案，死者阿旦杜亞父親沙裏布於6月20日報警後，政府宣布開檔重新調查這宗發生在12年前的殘忍謀殺炸屍命案。<br />\n<br />\n原文係殘體但唔係支媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星馬都係用殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁轉正體可能有錯唔check啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/阿尔丹杜雅&middot;沙丽布谋杀案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%98%BF%E5%B0%94%E4%B8%B9%E6%9D%9C%E9%9B%85%C2%B7%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%BD%E5%B8%83%E8%B0%8B%E6%9D%80%E6%A1%88&d=Hbpg4j%2F5NhQYtgRbQA9tJL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=02760235\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/阿尔丹杜雅&middot;沙丽布谋杀案</a><br />\n<br />\n原來有單咁既案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4e48ce32cbf723d550da64426b1d1b1041f336","tid":727761,"uid":38255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T19:00:56.000Z","m